solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public String originalDigits(String s) {--newline--        int[] count = new int[10];--newline--        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++){--newline--            char c = s.charAt(i);--newline--            if (c == 'z') count[0]++;--newline--            if (c == 'w') count[2]++;--newline--            if (c == 'x') count[6]++;--newline--            if (c == 's') count[7]++; //7-6--newline--            if (c == 'g') count[8]++;--newline--            if (c == 'u') count[4]++; --newline--            if (c == 'f') count[5]++; //5-4--newline--            if (c == 'h') count[3]++; //3-8--newline--            if (c == 'i') count[9]++; //9-8-5-6--newline--            if (c == 'o') count[1]++; //1-0-2-4--newline--        }--newline--        count[7] -= count[6];--newline--        count[5] -= count[4];--newline--        count[3] -= count[8];--newline--        count[9] = count[9] - count[8] - count[5] - count[6];--newline--        count[1] = count[1] - count[0] - count[2] - count[4];--newline--        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();--newline--        for (int i = 0; i <= 9; i++){--newline--            for (int j = 0; j < count[i]; j++){--newline--                sb.append(i);--newline--            }--newline--        }--newline--        return sb.toString();--newline--    }--newline--}
